{"tid":488939,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(time alter?)(圍毆案)事主自稱與常人不同：望落去係慢鏡","createTime":"2017-12-04T07:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T10:22:19.000Z","uid":6327,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8268471ecf90d5934797c3780c42d99359b557fd","tid":488939,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171204/s00001/1512368715180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171204%2Fs00001%2F1512368715180&d=fvfZ903C9G%2BtEKZ90tb7w6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ba47566d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171204%2Fs00001%2F1512368715180&h=0d1c6b54\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171204/s00001/1512368715180</a><br />\n一名男動漫迷在去年情人節突收邀約「開房」，惟疑遭設局被圍毆。事主今繼續接受盤問，<span style=\"color: red;\">形容自己與一般人不同，即使施襲者攻擊速度快，但「望落去係慢鏡」，能準確記得第2被告「白毛」打了他頭部55次、腰部20次等。</span>事主又表示受襲期間附近有很多市民表現「冷血無情」，即使他曾叫救命亦沒有人理會。<br />\n<br />\n事主羅浩峰表示，當日在九龍灣零碳天地時被「白毛」用木劍打他頭部55次、腰部20次、腿13次。被問到為何能準確記得，羅則回應指「我望落去係慢鏡」，無論速度多快都能看到，「反應力快同慢令我知道確實次數」，正常人看不到。羅又表示當時頭、腰、小腿等部位都感到痛楚，甚至覺得「暈暈地」。<br />\n<br />\n羅憶述在零碳天地受襲及拍片之處，約兩米外有一間半露天咖啡店，當時有5男5女及3名嬰兒在店內，羅曾向他們叫「救命」，但沒有人理睬他。羅又指約3米外有兩名公園的管理員坐着，看見他被打仍若無其事，「嘻嘻哈哈傾計」。羅續指當時亦有不少市民經過，惟全都看到他被打後就走。他說：「香港市民不嬲都係咁。」<br />\n<br />\n羅曾經在被「脅持」回九展時逃跑，惟被追回及毆打。羅指當時「白毛」曾用拳頭打他的頭部15次，又用木劍「篤」他心口正中位置，「意圖想殺死我」。他指被襲期間面朝天倒地，曾伸手出來大呼「救我呀救我呀」，惟沒人理會。<br />\n<br />\n羅期後聲稱被帶去乘巴士到尖沙嘴再被打，被問到曾否向公園管理員或巴士司機求救要求幫忙報警，羅則指沒有。<br />\n<br />\n第2被告「白毛」代表律師指，「白毛」從沒有與羅有身體接觸，亦從沒有阻止他離開身旁，甚或偷走羅的充電器。羅不同意，反問：「你咁樣講，係咪失咗記憶。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://orig10.deviantart.net/ba93/f/2016/208/c/9/r8oau__by_dynamo1212-dabkcjk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forig10.deviantart.net%2Fba93%2Ff%2F2016%2F208%2Fc%2F9%2Fr8oau__by_dynamo1212-dabkcjk.gif&h=cb82d9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://78.media.tumblr.com/d24dd17922e8c1c8f5510ebe8eae313e/tumblr_mj0qs9BuKN1s0bxg2o3_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fd24dd17922e8c1c8f5510ebe8eae313e%2Ftumblr_mj0qs9BuKN1s0bxg2o3_400.gif&h=2bbd41bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e4620e94924826a643b9422ea22b81fe32b4baa","tid":488939,"uid":86943,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"個頭俾人踢得多，傻咗"},{"pid":"3070e09b0ce71446598aa30da8fc61613c0b96d4","tid":488939,"uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1c0af996ce283e5ed14cf5ef3b567f2c80d11e","tid":488939,"uid":1972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"中咗黃金體驗"},{"pid":"c532099726e36bd7bfa308430b2e24f9a9594701","tid":488939,"uid":51978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/IMa1QoEuac4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIMa1QoEuac4&d=fvfZ903C9G%2BtEKZ90tb7w6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=1cbed958\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/IMa1QoEuac4</a>"},{"pid":"f2d1af45f730308bbbf5686e6592be20941dcbb9","tid":488939,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個頭俾人踢得多，傻咗</blockquote><br />\nlink左去根源"},{"pid":"31fa4bee58de18a8de3974e0c46f87478ef9b663","tid":488939,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"動漫迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5ea885d58857ad2a6677d03a5519e3ecea3c5a","tid":488939,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20